  "short_description": "48V 2A 96W Power Supply Unit with Plug",
  "description": "The MikroTik Power Adapter 48V 2A 96W is a high-performance power supply designed for MikroTik devices that support 48 V PoE output, such as the hEX PoE and CRS112-8P-4S-IN. It delivers a stable 48 V DC output at 2 A, providing a total power capacity of 96 W for efficient and reliable operation of your network equipment. Compared to the previous 48POW model (48 V 1.46 A 70 W), this upgraded adapter supplies 30% more current, allowing more power to each connected port and ensuring better performance for multiple PoE devices. Built with durability and safety in mind, the adapter provides consistent power even under continuous load. Ideal for professional network setups or home installations requiring dependable PoE power, the MikroTik 48V 2A 96W adapter ensures stable performance, improved efficiency, and long-lasting reliability for your MikroTik infrastructure.",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Power Adapter",
      "text": "The MikroTik Power Adapter 48V 2A 96W is a high-performance power supply designed for MikroTik devices that support 48 V PoE output, such as the hEX PoE and CRS112-8P-4S-IN. It delivers a stable 48 V DC output at 2 A, providing a total power capacity of 96 W for efficient and reliable operation of your network equipment. Compared to the previous 48POW model (48 V 1.46 A 70 W), this upgraded adapter supplies 30% more current, allowing more power to each connected port and ensuring better performance for multiple PoE devices. Built with durability and safety in mind, the adapter provides consistent power even under continuous load. Ideal for professional network setups or home installations requiring dependable PoE power, the MikroTik 48V 2A 96W adapter ensures stable performance, improved efficiency, and long-lasting reliability for your MikroTik infrastructure."
    }
